title: Did Blac Chyna Overreact ?
itunes:title: Did Blac Chyna Overreact ?
description:
Wednesday 4/3- Even though the stroller Blac Chyna threw did not hit anyone during the situation, it definitely did some damage to her money now, because her reaction led her to lose her deal with the stroller company "Mommiie". But the real question is was it worth it? So we opened up the phone lines to see if our listeners thought Blac Chyna overreacted, or was she showing her responsibility as a mother. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the YouTube shooter and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
